===Noun phrase===
'''car bomb'''

#An automobile laden with a very large amount of explosives, and detonated by a variety of means such as a [[timer]], [[remote contro]]l, or a [[suicide bomber]].
#An explosive attached to the fuel tank of an automobile, typically triggered by the ignition.
#[[Flatulence]] in an enclosed automobile (i.e. when inclement weather precludes open windows.)

